data.description: Are you looking for a serene setting with an incredible location?  Custom built 5 Bedroom, 3.5 Bath home with finished basement and covered rear porch in heart of Oconee County! This home has hardwood floors throughout the main level in the foyer, formal dining room, great room, kitchen, keeping room and master bedroom. Exquisite granite in this beautiful gourmet kitchen with farm sink and high-end stainless steel appliances. Great room has a coffered ceiling and a gas log fireplace. The large kitchen and keeping room has another brick fireplace with gas logs. Upgraded flooring throughout. Large master bedroom is on the main floor and overlooks the secluded backyard. The master bath has dual granite vanities and a custom tiled shower and separate soaking tub. There are 3 spacious bedrooms upstairs with lots of closet space. The basement is mostly finished with a media room with big screen TV and surround sound, rec room perfect for a home gym so you can stay in good health. The spacious bedroom and bath along with an office complete the finished basement. A cozy covered porch and enlarged deck off the back of the home overlooks the large back yard. The patio below has been extended and makes for another great outdoor gathering area. The sodded back yard extends through the trees and has a masonry patio fire pit area with electricity. Wired speakers throughout the home and covered porch great for relaxing while listening to your favorite artist. All of this on a 1.47 acre lot in desirable Oconee County, in a highly sought after school system. Ryland Hills has a country feel just minutes from downtown Watkinsville and Wire Park. Only 12 minutes to UGA Vet School. Amenities include a swimming pool and tennis courts. Hurry and schedule your private tour today!
